1. Nadam se da ćeš mi *poverovati* da nisam lagala. (I hope you will *believe* me that I didn't lie.)
2. Moram *poverovati* da mi je bila potrebna promena. (I have to *believe* that I needed a change.)
3. Nisam mogao *poverovati* da je to stvarno istina. (I couldn't *believe* it was really true.)
4. Želim da mi *poveruješ* kada kažem da ti želim samo najbolje. (I want you to *believe* me when I say I want only the best for you.)
5. Oni nisu želeli da mi *poveruju* sve dok nisam pokazala dokaz. (They didn't want to *believe* me until I showed them proof.)
6. Ne mogu da *poverujem* koliko je ovo ukusno. (I can't *believe* how delicious this is.)
7. Molim te, *poveruj* mi da ovo radim za tvoje dobro. (Please, *believe* me that I'm doing this for your own good.)
8. Da li mi *veruješ* da sam upravo čuo najneverovatniju priču? (Do you *believe* me that I just heard the most unbelievable story?) 
9. Znam da ćeš mi *poverovati* kada budeš video dokaze. (I know you will *believe* me when you see the evidence.)
10. Bilo mi je teško da *poverujem* u njihovu iskrenost nakon što su me prevarili. (It was hard for me to *believe* in their honesty after they cheated me.)